ight, but it is important nonetheless.<br>
<br>
KCoG is not a marketing organization. KCoG wont do all the work getting all the information and getting people excited about any raid. They only provide the leadership and hosting ability to do one of these raids.<br>
<br>
/rant on<br>
<br>
YOU have to spread the word about this. If you don't, noone else will. You need to make hotkeys, guildmotd's, post on your website, whatever. You are the marketer. If YOU don't get people psyched about this, keep them interested, and promote this, we will probably not go forward.<br>
<br>
Don't Wait Till The Last Minute! We have four months, yeah okay great. But, that's four months of promotion that we need. Post strategy articles, have a forum setup just for VS stuff. Get them discussing it.<br>
<br>
If you know of a guild that is not on VS Rotation, let them know about it. '/tell guild_leader01 Hey, KCoG has signed up for VS Rotation. Be interested in helping?'<br>
<br>
Bottom line guys, if you don't support this within your guild, it will fail. KCoG isn't a guild who allows people to join their raids. It's a council of guilds with a leadership that you support. Without You KCoG wouldn't exist.<br>
<br>
